				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Decided to try the Scholar.
<br />
Nice to make your own spells ya know,
<br />
and you can earn a decent buck on the way as well.
<br />

<br />
What drop-kicked me in the face was this:
<br />

<br />
Some 10 hour exp-grinding session later.....
<br />

<br />
Ding lvl 11. Got the Scholars Essentials Vol 11.
<br />
( after 2h looking for them all over Freeport )
<br />

<br />
/scribe
<br />

<br />
Fucking great! Blaze AppIII , Tellurian Recruit AppIII etc etc +++
<br />
Still some recipes missing, but damn I am well on the way here....
<br />

<br />
So I run eagerly down to my engraved desk to crank out
<br />
some of these great spells.....
<br />

<br />
So lets see....what do we need here....
<br />

<br />
Iron Gaul Ink, Check.
<br />
Maple Quill, err
<br />
Cailun Paper....what the..
<br />
Incense, check.
<br />

<br />
Cailun Paper? Wtf?
<br />
Maple Quills? WTF?
<br />

<br />
I mean, what the fuck?
<br />

<br />
Are the scholar supposed to be a fucking woodworker as well
<br />
or what part did I miss?
<br />

<br />
So I log off and go over to EQ2-artisan:
<br />

<br />
Yes. Woodworking lvl 10.
<br />
You chose your path (scholar) so fuck off. Sorry.
<br />

<br />
Well, what I did was make another char, grind the way to
<br />
lvl 10 craftsman, and make the fucking Maple Quills.
<br />

<br />
No big deal, really  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Just a 'warning' to those of you that are taking on crafting:
<br />

<br />
You are in for a big surprise  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.eq2-artisan.com" target="_blank">www.eq2-artisan.com</a>
<br />

<br />
Thank me later  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v514/Yuizling/boobs.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Like it or not, boobs are back.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
