				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's not a suprise if you have been following eq2 =)
<br />

<br />
Part of the tradeskill design is that you will need the other classes to make stuff.
<br />

<br />
You need a Outfitter, they need a Scholar. Both of ya'll need a Supplier.
<br />

<br />
Every tradeskill class needs other classes to make stuff.
<br />

<br />
It makes sense to me... =)<br />_________________<br />-Laeelin
<br />
65 Necro
