<br />

<br />
I've been learning over the last few days just how forked up the drop rate is on Adept 1 spells.  I mean it COSTS me 16sp to make some App 3 spells, and yet people are selling Adept 1 spells for 5sp because the drop rate is so damned high.
<br />

<br />
I've never....not ONCE....asked for a nerf.  But they really gotta nerf the drop rate on *some* Adept 1 spells, and *increase* the drop rate on others.
<br />

<br />
As was mentioned above, some Adept 1 spells will drop all damned day, but good luck finding an Adept 1 summoner's pet.<br />_________________<br />EQ1:  Mujahid Mukhtaar - Arch Lich, Solusek Ro (Retired)
